### Combining Classes

You can combine multiple classes for unique effects:

```html
<!-- Rainbow + Large -->
<button class="cfl-btn cfl-btn--rainbow cfl-btn--lg">Epic Button</button>

<!-- Primary base + Bouncy animation -->
<button class="cfl-btn cfl-btn--primary cfl-btn--bouncy cfl-btn--md">Bouncy Primary</button>

<!-- Ghost + Pulse effect -->
<button class="cfl-btn cfl-btn--ghost cfl-btn--pulse cfl-btn--sm">Subtle Pulse</button>
```

### Pro Tips

1. **Dark backgrounds** - Neon, glitch, and eldritch buttons look best on dark backgrounds
2. **Accessibility** - Fun buttons should still have good contrast and focus states
3. **Performance** - Limit animated buttons on pages with many elements
4. **Context** - Match button style to your content's mood

